---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="页面未找到" description="请求的页面不存在。">
  <div class="stack-lg article-shell">
    <p class="eyebrow">404</p>
    <h1>这里暂时没有内容。</h1>
    <p class="lede">页面可能尚未迁移，或者地址已经变化。迁移旧站时会为已有公开链接建立兼容映射。</p>
    <div class="button-row"><a class="button" href="/">返回首页</a><a class="button secondary" href="/blog/">查看博客</a></div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
